Build the tests with the following commands:

  mkdir build && cd build
  cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug .
  make -j8

On MacOs, install gcc-13 and g++-13 with homebrew.
Then, use these compilers in the cmake step:

  cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -DCMAKE_C_COMPILER=gcc-13 -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=g++-13 .
